{"tid":1448213,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"葵芳地鐵站可能有殘留山埃，如非必要香港市民請勿前往","createTime":"2019-08-11T16:27:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T16:39:12.000Z","uid":269825,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"767fc3c660e4be37c8b70280d6be2eab68af4a45","tid":1448213,"uid":269825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:27:06.000Z","msg":"[請廣傳，出自醫學院博士的緊急通知] 葵芳地鐵站可能有殘留山埃，如非必要香港市民請勿前往<br />\n<br />\n警察於8月11日葵芳地鐵站發射疑似過期催淚彈，會釋放出氧化山埃(cyanide oxides),可經皮膚及呼吸道吸收。<br />\n<br />\n如該化學物經呼吸系列入，與水份作化學作用會變成氫化山埃(hydrogen cyanide)，是納粹當年大規模殺害猶太人之最有效毒藥。<br />\n<br />\n由於地鐵室內空間尤其不通風，毒素會殘留在地鐵站建築物內部。所有人士，特別是長者，孕婦，小孩，長期病患及呼吸疾病人士更應遠離該地鐵站，直至港鐵完成毒理化驗證實安全為止。"},{"pid":"7714677ada475754bb7fdc060762c7aec2027567","tid":1448213,"uid":78913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:29:43.000Z","msg":"黑警喪心病狂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />簡直係想殺人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52da4d37221f8cef72d824a6782fc0eabbdbd2d6","tid":1448213,"uid":43647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:29:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"35deccfe50cb98f9205b37c1cb331c86db5c0b6f","tid":1448213,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:30:06.000Z","msg":"仲有太古站"},{"pid":"f0eec822ce84815a760e8387b8771b0d9ccd5680","tid":1448213,"uid":202889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:30:09.000Z","msg":"文宣圖 裡面冇嘅可以自己upload上去<br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/drive/u/0/folders/1699DS2mdmfWd1-wfBVoAiVpu6SP2rqpt\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fdrive%2Fu%2F0%2Ffolders%2F1699DS2mdmfWd1-wfBVoAiVpu6SP2rqpt&d=4tZOiqwfeINLG3hE5eaPvJR%2B4kUINcy65scadR%2F1ewI%3D&h=fe7507c1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/drive/u/0/folders/1699DS2mdmfWd1-wfBVoAiVpu6SP2rqpt</a>"},{"pid":"901ed6679148841899482ebf0ae558f260d5372a","tid":1448213,"uid":